V<<sidebar "Withdrawing from your program">>\u000aWe hope you won't have to withdraw from your program. But if you must, please note the following:\u000a\u000a<<if $vanderbilt>>|box|k\u000a|!Withdrawal Deadline|<<if $maymester>>You need to withdraw by the Withdrawal Deadline specified on the [[Maymester/Summer Sessions page|http://www.vanderbilt.edu/summer/maysession/abroad-listings.php]]<<else>>In your GEO account ([[log in|https://webapp.mis.vanderbilt.edu/studioabroad/index.cfm?FuseAction=Security.ExistingUserLogin]]), you will find a Withdrawal Deadline. You need to withdraw by this date<</if>> to avoid penalties.|\u000a|!Communication|You must withdraw with GEO in writing.<<if $facultyled>> Be sure to also notify your course instructor/faculty leader<</if>>|\u000a|!Potential Costs|If you withdraw after the stated Withdrawal Deadline, <<if $maymester>>the VU college offering the course<<else>>GEO<</if>> may bill a monetary penalty to your VU student account. Such penalties generally increase as the departure date gets closer. If you must withdraw, do so as early as you can!|<<else>>|box|k\u000a|!Withdrawal Deadline|In your GEO account ([[log in|https://webapp.mis.vanderbilt.edu/studioabroad/index.cfm?FuseAction=Security.ExistingUserLogin]]), you will find a Withdrawal Deadline. You need to withdraw by this date to avoid penalties.|\u000a|!Communication|You must withdraw with GEO in writing. If you applied to one of Vanderbilt's partner organizations (e.g., CIEE, CET, IFSA-Butler), you must contact //both// the partner and GEO to communicate your decision.|\u000a|!Potential Costs|If you withdraw after the stated Withdrawal Deadline, GEO may bill a monetary penalty to your VU student account. Such penalties generally increase as the departure date gets closer. If you must withdraw, do so as early as you can!|\u000a|!Obligations|If you signed an agreement with one of our partners (CIEE, CET, IFSA-Butler, etc.), you will have to pay their deposit //even if// you withdraw before the GEO Withdrawal Deadline. GEO will pay this for you and bill your student account.|<</if>>\u005c\u000a\u000a<<if $maymester>>Please read the full [[Maymester Withdrawal policy|http://www.vanderbilt.edu/summer/maysession/abroad-listings.php]]<<else>>Please read GEO's full [[Withdrawal Instructions and Policies|https://webapp.mis.vanderbilt.edu/studioabroad/index.cfm?FuseAction=PublicDocuments.View&File_ID=2587]]<</if>>.\u000a\u000a<<segue "Preparation and responsibilities">>\u005c
